  <brief_title>Rituximab After Autologous Stem Cell Transplant for Relapsed B-cell Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Trial Of C2B8 Monoclonal Antibody Following High Dose Therapy And Autografting In B-Cell Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma</official_title>
